last_episode_to_air.name: Cake Expectations
last_episode_to_air.overview: Lulu has to do a presentation in class on a Victorian novel, but she hasn't read the book.

name: Jinx
overview: Comedy drama about a girl with a magical cookbook. It feels to Lulu as if her life cannot get any worse, when a visitor takes her on a magical adventure.

episodes.name: Baker House Blend
episodes.overview: An extraordinary visitor takes Lulu on an exciting and magical adventure.

episodes.name: Dead and Butter Pudding
episodes.overview: Lulu is babysitting her step-brother when he accidentally eats some magic bread and butter pudding and turns into a zombie. Lulu has to find a way to stop him, but all he wants to do is eat her brains!

episodes.name: Cookie Chips
episodes.overview: Cookie's latest recipe provides Lulu with three clones of Chip to help her prepare for the school fashion show. But she has promised Frenchy she will do it without help from the magic cookbook and it is only a matter of time before Frenchy gets suspicious.

episodes.name: Sweet Taste of Success
episodes.overview: Penny challenges Lulu to beat her in a geography test. But, using one of Cookie's recipes, Lulu mind reads Frenchy's answers and gets top marks. Mysteriously, Frenchy gets bottom marks. Penny is clearly up to no good.

episodes.name: The Chip Files
episodes.overview: Chip believes aliens exist, Lulu knows they don't. Frenchy will believe anything Chip believes and Torquil will believe anything as long as it impresses Frenchy. But when Cookie gets involved and turns Chip into an alien, nobody knows quite what to believe!

episodes.name: A Slice of the Future
episodes.overview: Fish and chips pizzas were never destined to be Mike's most successful creation for the cafe, but, thanks to Cookie, they enjoy a brief spell of popularity with his customers before everyone turns against them again.

episodes.name: Proof of the Pudding
episodes.overview: Lulu engineers a reconciliation between her father and his long-estranged brother Paolo.

episodes.name: A Slight Hiccup
episodes.overview: It is Lulu's birthday and Minty's surprise gives her anything but pleasure.

episodes.name: Ratatorquil
episodes.overview: It is Valentine's Day and Lulu does not have a date, but Cookie has a solution.

episodes.name: Minty Freshman
episodes.overview: Lulu volunteers herself and Frenchy for the school talent show.

episodes.name: Humble Pie and Mash
episodes.overview: Lulu tries to turn her father into a television performer and ends up a celebrity herself.

episodes.name: Flavour of the Month
episodes.overview: Cookie provides a recipe which makes the world agree with everything Lulu says.

episodes.name: Cake Expectations
episodes.overview: Lulu has to do a presentation in class on a Victorian novel, but she hasn't read the book.
